<li id="cite_note-6"><b><a href="#cite_ref-6" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal">D.R. Kuhn (1997). "<a href="http://csrc.nist.gov/groups/SNS/rbac/documents/design_implementation/kuhn-97.pdf" class="external text" title="http://csrc.nist.gov/groups/SNS/rbac/documents/design_implementation/kuhn-97.pdf" rel="nofollow">Mutual Exclusion of Roles as a Means of Implementing Separation of Duty in Role-Based Access Control Systems</a>" (<a href="/wiki/PDF" title="PDF" class="mw-redirect">PDF</a>). <i>2nd ACM Workshop Role-Based Access Control</i>: 23 - 30.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=proceeding&amp;rft.btitle=2nd+ACM+Workshop+Role-Based+Access+Control&amp;rft.atitle=Mutual+Exclusion+of+Roles+as+a+Means+of+Implementing+Separation+of+Duty+in+Role-Based+Access+Control+Systems&amp;rft.au=D.R.+Kuhn&amp;rft.date=1997&amp;rft.pages=23+-+30&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fcsrc.nist.gov%2Fgroups%2FSNS%2Frbac%2Fdocuments%2Fdesign_implementation%2Fkuhn-97.pdf"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-7"><b><a href="#cite_ref-7" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal">Ninghui Li, Ziad Bizri, and Mahesh V. Tripunitara . Tripunitara (2004). "<a href="http://portal.acm.org/citation.cfm?id=1030091" class="external text" title="http://portal.acm.org/citation.cfm?id=1030091" rel="nofollow">On mutually exclusive roles and separation-of-duty,</a>" (<a href="/wiki/PDF" title="PDF" class="mw-redirect">PDF</a>). <i>11th ACM conference on Computer and Communications Security</i>: 42 - 51.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=proceeding&amp;rft.btitle=11th+ACM+conference+on+Computer+and+Communications+Security&amp;rft.atitle=On+mutually+exclusive+roles+and+separation-of-duty%2C&amp;rft.au=Ninghui+Li%2C+Ziad+Bizri%2C+and+Mahesh+V.+Tripunitara+.+Tripunitara&amp;rft.date=2004&amp;rft.pages=42+-+51&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fportal.acm.org%2Fcitation.cfm%3Fid%3D1030091"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-8"><b><a href="#cite_ref-8" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal">Sandhu, R., Ferraiolo, D.F. and Kuhn, D.R. (July 2000). "<a href="http://csrc.nist.gov/rbac/sandhu-ferraiolo-kuhn-00.pdf" class="external text" title="http://csrc.nist.gov/rbac/sandhu-ferraiolo-kuhn-00.pdf" rel="nofollow">The NIST Model for Role Based Access Control: Toward a Unified Standard</a>" (<a href="/wiki/PDF" title="PDF" class="mw-redirect">PDF</a>). <i>5th ACM Workshop Role-Based Access Control</i>: 47-63.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=proceeding&amp;rft.btitle=5th+ACM+Workshop+Role-Based+Access+Control&amp;rft.atitle=The+NIST+Model+for+Role+Based+Access+Control%3A+Toward+a+Unified+Standard&amp;rft.au=Sandhu%2C+R.%2C+Ferraiolo%2C+D.F.+and+Kuhn%2C+D.R.&amp;rft.date=2000&amp;rft.pages=47-63&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fcsrc.nist.gov%2Frbac%2Fsandhu-ferraiolo-kuhn-00.pdf"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
